{"lastModified":1770975747176,"uri":"c::44417918732::vessel::d60dec20-c6f1-11f0-aa89-47dd760498d9","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Italy\n\nThe Prestige M48 Italia IV is a luxury power catamaran launched in 2025, designed to offer a sophisticated cruising experience along the Italian and Mediterranean coasts. Measuring 14.79 meters long and 6 meters wide, this vessel offers generous interior and exterior space, with superior stability thanks to its multi-hull configuration. Equipped with twin Volvo Penta D4 engines, 320 horsepower each, a V-Drive system, and a joystick for easy maneuvering, it offers a cruising speed of around 15 knots and a top speed of approximately 20 knots. Its range can reach 600 nautical miles at 8 knots, with fuel efficiency 20% higher than a monohull of the same size.\n\nThe interior of the M48 Italia IV is designed to accommodate up to 8 guests in 4 double cabins, each with a private bathroom, as well as a crew cabin with a separate bathroom. Exterior spaces include a large, covered flybridge with a sunbathing area, a U-shaped sofa, and a removable table; an electric, multi-position swim platform, also ideal for use as a beach club or for the tender; a forward sunbathing area with reclining backrests; and a spacious cockpit with a wooden table and teak flooring.","blueprint":{"name":"ITALIA IV","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d60dec20-c6f1-11f0-aa89-47dd760498d9::assets::59ee4831-c6f9-11f0-9d6e-6ff4a43d5b09/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d60dec20-c6f1-11f0-aa89-47dd760498d9::assets::59f04400-c6f9-11f0-9d6f-6ff4a43d5b09/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d60dec20-c6f1-11f0-aa89-47dd760498d9::assets::59ec2551-c6f9-11f0-8ba5-476b83e81b50/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d60dec20-c6f1-11f0-aa89-47dd760498d9::assets::59ec7370-c6f9-11f0-8ba5-476b83e81b50/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d60dec20-c6f1-11f0-aa89-47dd760498d9::assets::59